[{"id":"VR252061","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\">Show all your work. Indicate clearly the methods you use, because you will be scored on the correctness of your methods as well as on the accuracy and completeness of your results and explanations.</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"passage\">\n<div class=\"prose style:1\">\n<p class=\"passage_para\">Many people who suffer from a common skin ailment decide to buy a generic brand skin cream instead of a name-brand skin cream because of cost savings. A skin doctor plans to investigate the following claim made in an advertisement.</p>\n\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"tgroup cols:1 colsep:0 rowsep:0\">\n\t<colgroup>\n\t\t<col class=\"colspec align:center colname:col1 colnum:1 colwidth:350\" />\n\t</colgroup>\n\t<tbody class=\"tbody\">\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">The generic brand of a skin cream is less effective in curing a common skin ailment than a name-brand skin cream.</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"passage_para\">The doctor is considering the following two options for the design of a study:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li class=\"list_paragraph\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">Option A:</span> Obtain <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"500\"><math alttext=\"500\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>500</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> volunteers from the population of people with the skin ailment who use the generic brand skin cream each day. Obtain <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"500\"><math alttext=\"500\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>500</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> volunteers from the population of people with the skin ailment who use the name-brand skin cream each day. Observe the number of people cured in each group after six months.</li>\n\t<li class=\"list_paragraph\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">Option B:</span> Randomly assign <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1,000\"><math alttext=\"1,000\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn><mtext>,000</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> volunteers with the skin ailment to one of two groups, each with <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"500\"><math alttext=\"500\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>500</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> people. Give the name-brand skin cream to one group to be used each day and the generic brand skin cream to the other group to be used each day. Observe the number of people cured in each group after six months.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"item_part part_id:a part_name:ExtendedText response_class:FreeResponse response_type:Essay\" id=\"a\">\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">(a) Give a reason why Option B is more appropriate than Option A for investigating the effectiveness of the skin cream. Justify your answer in the context of the problem.</p>\n</div>\n","rubricRef":"VR252061_rubric"},{"id":"VR252061","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<div class=\"item_part part_id:b part_name:ExtendedText response_class:FreeResponse response_type:Essay\" id=\"b\"><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">(b) Describe a modification to Option B or identify an alternate design that would improve the study. Explain why your answer would be an improvement.</p></div>\n","rubricRef":"VR252061_rubric"},{"id":"VR252061","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<div class=\"item_part part_id:c part_name:ExtendedText response_class:FreeResponse response_type:Essay\" id=\"c\">\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">The doctor conducted the investigation using the design described in Option B. The results are shown in the following table.</p>\n\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\">\n<table class=\"tgroup cols:4\">\n\t<tbody class=\"tbody\">\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1 text-center\">&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2 text-center\">Generic brand</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3 text-center\">Name brand</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col4 text-center\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">Total</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1 text-center\">Cured skin ailment</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"244\"><math alttext=\"244\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>244</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"299\"><math alttext=\"299\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>299</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col4 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"543\"><math alttext=\"543\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>543</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1 text-center\">Did not cure skin ailment</td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"256\"><math alttext=\"256\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>256</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"201\"><math alttext=\"201\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>201</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col4 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"457\"><math alttext=\"457\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>457</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col1 text-center\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">Total</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col2 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"500\"><math alttext=\"500\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>500</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col3 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"500\"><math alttext=\"500\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>500</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t\t<td class=\"entry colname:col4 text-center\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1,000\"><math alttext=\"1,000\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn><mtext>,000</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">(c) For the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1,000\"><math alttext=\"1,000\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn><mtext>,000</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> people in the study, is the cure of the skin ailment independent of the brand of skin cream used? Justify your answer using values from the table. Do not perform an inferential procedure.</p>\n</div>\n","rubricRef":"VR252061_rubric"},{"id":"VR252061","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<div class=\"item_part part_id:d part_name:ExtendedText response_class:FreeResponse response_type:Essay\" id=\"d\"><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">An appropriate hypothesis test will be conducted to determine whether the sample data provide convincing statistical evidence to support the claim about skin cream made in the advertisement.</p><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">(d) State, <span class=\"formatted_text text_decoration:underline\">in words</span>, the hypotheses for the appropriate test.</p></div>\n","rubricRef":"VR252061_rubric"},{"id":"VR252061","type":"longtextV2","stimulusHtml":"<div class=\"item_part part_id:e part_name:ExtendedText response_class:FreeResponse response_type:Essay\" id=\"e\"><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Assume all conditions for the test of the hypotheses from part (d) are met. The test was conducted, and the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"p\"><math alttext=\"p\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>-value was less than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"0.01\"><math alttext=\"0.01\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>0.01</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">(e) At the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> percent level of significance, what can the doctor conclude about the claim made about skin cream in the advertisement? Explain your answer.</p></div>\n","rubricRef":"VR252061_rubric"}]